{"TopicId":136526,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Kerbal Drifting!","CreatedByName":"Heckspress","CreatedById":8020,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-09T16:22:37Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Heckspress","CreatedById":8020,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-09T16:22:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a thing that I\u0027ve been just having so much fun with. You reduce the friction control to 0.1 and it suddenly becomes a drift car!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe vehicle in the video is a tweaked version of ScriptKitt3h\u0027s Badger ATV. 1.1 is still bugging out and kerbs keep popping out of seats.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/ayozkKwVvd8?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YoeriCookie","CreatedById":119887,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-09T17:40:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhats going on with your cursor there?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Heckspress","CreatedById":8020,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-09T17:41:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222504836\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136526\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460223615\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022119887\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022YoeriCookie\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, YoeriCookie said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhats going on with your cursor there?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know. Maybe it\u0027s my recording software?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ScriptKitt3h","CreatedById":82780,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-09T19:38:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow, nice drifting! If there\u0027s any bugs come 1.1\u0027s full release, rest assured I\u0027ll fix them on the 1.1 version of the Badger.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOtherwise, I\u0027m glad to see it works in 1.1 and that you\u0027re enjoying it. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}